{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: "Lee said you wanted to talk to me about what's been going on, Commandant?", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: 'What exactly do you mean? I hope we can settle it during this break before I return to work on the documents.', 4: '1'}
{2: "Liv, you've been acting like someone else.", 3: '7', 4: 'N-nothing...', 5: '8'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: 'Someone else? Do you mean my appearance?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: 'Commandant, suppressing your problems will only allow them to fester and create more troubles in the future.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: 'Am I sensing concerns about how my personality has changed?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: 'I understand that you will worry about my attitude and approach, Commandant.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: "Let's put it this way. I haven't become someone else. I've merely adapted to suit our situation better.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'What situation?', 3: '13', 4: 'I think I prefer the old you.', 5: '14'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: 'Combat, support, exploration, work. Everything.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: 'Nothing would be done if I kept going on like that...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: 'Anyway, I should go back to taking care of the dormitory and the document from Babylonia.', 4: '1'}
{2: "Isn't that my job?", 3: '17', 4: "You're helping me on those too, Liv?", 5: '18'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: "We don't have to bother you with this kind of trivial work, Commandant. I'll take care of the documents.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: "Of course. I don't think you'll have time to worry about them when you have the crucial job of commanding, Commandant.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: "Commandant, I hope you aren't asking for those jobs back.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: "This is something I want to do. And I'll finish what I started properly.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: 'Please trust me.', 4: '1'}
{2: "...Don't overexert yourself.", 3: '23', 4: 'I see.', 5: '24'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: "I'll pay attention to it.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: "Then please disconnect and rest up, Commandant. It's getting late.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: 'I should return to my work.', 4: '1'}
